This is a custom distribution of OGRE, (Object-Oriented Graphics Rendering
Engine), version 1.7.0, a scene-oriented and flexible 3D engine.

This distribution includes a custom CMake-based build system tailored to fit in
the Athena Game Framework.


License
-------

OGRE's license is unchanged: this library is released under the MIT License.

The license of OGRE is contained in the file 'COPYING'.


Submodules
----------

This distribution use zlib, zziplib, FreeImage and FreeType as a GIT submodules.
To download them, do:

	$ git submodule init
	$ git submodule update


Compilation
-----------

It is recommended to compile the library in a separate folder. Here's how I do it:

	$ mkdir build
	$ cd build
	$ cmake ..
	$ make
